s=177–182 |doi=10.1038/nature13316 |accessdate=16 July 2014 |archive-date=2017-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170629130537/http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v509/n7499/full/nature13316.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="HS-20140507">{{cite web |last=Aguilar |first=David A. |last2=Pulliam |first2=Christine |title=Astronomers Create First Realistic Virtual Universe - Release No.: 2014-10 |url=http://www.cfa.harvard.edu/news/2014-10 |date=7 May 2014 |work=[[Harvard-Smithsonian_Center_for_Astrophysics|Harvard-Smithsonian Center for Astrophysics]] |accessdate=16 July 2014 |archive-date=2018-07-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180704123820/https://www.cfa.harvard.edu/news/2014-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="NYT-20140716">{{cite news |last=Overbye |first=Dennis |authorlink=Dennis Overbye |title=Stalking the Shadow Universe |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/07/16/science/space/stalking-the-shadow-universe.html |work=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]] |date=16 July 2014 |accessdate=16 July 2014 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112012004/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/07/16/science/space/stalking-the-shadow-universe.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="NASA-20140512">{{cite web |authors=Nemiroff, Robert; Bonnell, Jerry; Newman, Phillip |title=Astronomy Picture of the Day - Illustris Simulation of the Universe |url=http://apod.nasa.gov/apod/ap140512.html |date=12 May 2014 |work=[[NASA|NASA]] |accessdate=16 July 2014 |archive-date=2021-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210314192332/https://apod.nasa.gov/apod/ap140512.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 回顧 ==
[[File:Large-scale_structure_formation.gif|thumb]]的[[可觀測宇宙#大尺度結構|大尺度結構]]模擬－類似於''揭示計畫''。]]

''揭示計畫''包括[[可觀測宇宙|大尺度結構]]、[[類比|類比]][[宇宙論|宇宙論的]] [[宇宙年表|宇宙演化]]，跨越从[[大霹靂|大霹靂]]的初始條件，一直到[[宇宙年齡|138億]]年之後的現代。為了更好的了解宇宙的性質，包括[[星系的形成和演化|星系形成]]、[[暗物質|暗物質]]和[[暗能量|暗能量]]，基於當前可用的最精確資料和演算法，建模與[[可觀測宇宙|可觀測宇宙]]比較<ref name="IP-20140614" /><ref name="ARX-20140514" /><ref name="ARX-20140515" /><ref name="NAT-20140508" /><ref name="HS-20140507" /><ref name="NYT-20140716" /><ref name="NASA-20140512" />。早期的结果在广泛的新闻报道之后的许多出版物<ref name="ARX-20140514" /><ref name="ARX-20140515" /><ref name="NAT-20140508" />中被描述<ref name="HS-20140507" /><ref name="NYT-20140716"/><ref name="NASA-20140512"/>。该项目公开发布了2015年4月的模拟产生的所有数据。
